<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FormBank - Home</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2E7D32 0%, #1B5E20 50%, #0D3D10 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .header {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #1B5E20;
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .header p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .nav-link {
            color: #2E7D32;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .nav-link:hover {
            background: #E8F5E9;
            color: #1B5E20;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .hero {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .hero h2 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .hero p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            background: #2E7D32;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(46, 125, 50, 0.4);
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background: #1B5E20;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(27, 94, 32, 0.5);
        }
        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .feature-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }
        .feature-card h3 {
            color: #2E7D32;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .feature-card p {
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .info-section {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .info-section h2 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #2E7D32;
        }
        .info-section ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .info-section li {
            padding: 12px 0;
            color: #666;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
            padding-left: 30px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .info-section li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .info-section li:before {
            content: "‚úì";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #2E7D32;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üè¶ FormBank</h1>
            <p>Welcome back, <strong><%= user %></strong></p>
            <div class="nav">
                <a href="/credit" class="nav-link">Credit System ‚Üí</a>
                <a href="/checks" class="nav-link">Checks ‚Üí</a>
                <a href="/logout" class="nav-link">Logout</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero">
            <h2>Loans &amp; Checks for Digipogs</h2>
            <p>
                FormBank is your gateway to flexible digipog loans and peer-to-peer checks. 
                Borrow digipogs with simple 20% interest and watch your credit limit grow‚Äîor 
                write checks to other users (or leave them open for anyone to redeem). Pay back 
                on your own terms and send digipogs with ease.
            </p>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                <a href="/credit" class="cta-button">Credit &amp; Loans</a>
                <a href="/checks" class="cta-button" style="background: #1B5E20;">Write a Check</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">üí∞</div>
                <h3>Simple Loans</h3>
                <p>
                    Borrow digipogs with a fixed 20% interest rate. Start with a 250 digipog limit 
                    and watch it grow as you build your credit history.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">üìà</div>
                <h3>Growing Limits</h3>
                <p>
                    Each time you successfully pay off a loan, your credit limit increases by 250 digipogs. 
                    Build your credit and unlock higher borrowing power.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">üí≥</div>
                <h3>Credit Balance</h3>
                <p>
                    Overpayments are automatically credited to your account for future loan repayments. 
                    Never lose a digipog - every payment counts.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">üìù</div>
                <h3>Write Checks</h3>
                <p>
                    Send digipogs to any user by writing a check to their Formbar user ID. A small fee 
                    (5% or 5 digipogs, whichever is greater) is charged when you write the check; the 
                    receiver gets the full amount.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">üé´</div>
                <h3>Blank Checks</h3>
                <p>
                    Leave the receiver blank to create a check anyone can redeem. Only the fee is charged 
                    when you write it; the amount transfers when someone opens the check status page first 
                    (logged in or with their user ID). Great for gifts or flexible payouts.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-section">
            <h2>How It Works</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Borrow:</strong> Request a loan up to your current credit limit (starts at 250 digipogs)</li>
                <li><strong>Receive:</strong> Get your digipogs instantly (after Formbar's 10% transfer tax)</li>
                <li><strong>Repay:</strong> Pay back your loan in full or partial payments at any time</li>
                <li><strong>Grow:</strong> Every time your total repayments reach your current credit limit, that limit increases by +250 digipogs</li>
                <li><strong>Track:</strong> View your loan history and credit status anytime</li>
                <li><strong>Write a check:</strong> Enter amount, your PIN, and optionally a receiver's Formbar user ID (or leave blank for anyone to redeem)</li>
                <li><strong>Check status:</strong> View check details and a QR code for the status URL; only sender, receiver, or redeemer can access the page</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="info-section">
            <h2>Important Notes</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Only one active loan allowed at a time</li>
                <li>20% interest is calculated on the principal amount</li>
                <li>Formbar applies a 10% tax on all transfers (this is automatic)</li>
                <li>You receive 90% of the loan amount, but owe the full principal + 20% interest</li>
                <li>Overpayments are credited to your account for future use</li>
                <li>Check fee: 5% of the amount or 5 digipogs, whichever is greater (you pay amount + fee; receiver gets the amount)</li>
                <li>Blank checks: fee is charged when you write; the amount is transferred when the first person redeems via the check status page</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>FormBank System - Built for Formbar</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
